{"tid":818073,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時同張寶兒拉埋天窗？袁偉豪:想搏多兩年","createTime":"2018-09-14T00:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T16:30:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0368118159dbefede1cd962fcabbcf217b0748","tid":818073,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180911/_2018091100572836472.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180911%2F_2018091100572836472.jpeg&h=67800354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁偉豪（Ben）及張寶兒出席新劇《鐵探》煞科宴，談及好友陳展鵬和單文柔宣布下月結婚，Ben與寶兒異口同聲送恭喜，稱也是從報道上得知。<br />\n<br />\n不過問到何時輪到他們兩人拉天窗？Ben表示想多拼搏1、2年，現階段以工作和家人為先，寶兒常伴他左右，彼此也明白方向，亦很享受。<br />\n<br />\n問到會否像陳展鵬一樣低調、只邀請親戚出席婚宴？他稱各人有各人的喜好，自己會順從長輩意願。"},{"pid":"d896f9a7e8f2ef0a3cfaa6f59d19386fd8e03885","tid":818073,"uid":799,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:20:14.000Z","msg":"娶個白痴妹短廿年命都唔掂"},{"pid":"8882bd3935fd3630f9ba8e6f767fe1604b2809a9","tid":818073,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c4a55f7151f092630195beada1d9eca1174a5c","tid":818073,"uid":65128,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:27:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5d7688f51448686ac32142a34f1e761c0eb677e","tid":818073,"uid":81569,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"成日懷疑佢唔係真心鐘意條女<br />\n又白痴又低b 應該成日頂唔順"},{"pid":"e48d136700d0f616c726a3356b1fe6d18157ff1a","tid":818073,"uid":209391,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:49:30.000Z","msg":"想扑多兩年咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"